01:04:27,669 --> 01:04:30,037
- ( beeping )
- 18th floor.

1175
01:04:30,070 --> 01:04:33,140
- 18th floor, now.
- Charlie!

1176
01:04:33,173 --> 01:04:36,477
- You surprised me.
- That was my intention.

1177
01:04:36,511 --> 01:04:41,014
I don't get a lot of visitors
up here. Please, sit down.

1178
01:04:46,253 --> 01:04:47,488
I'll make this brief.

1179
01:04:47,522 --> 01:04:50,491
I think that's probably best.

