the amount of the moneys unaccounted
for on your balance sheet.

1188
01:05:26,561 --> 01:05:31,031
Oh, my goodness. Almost
$400,000, Charlie.

1189
01:05:31,064 --> 01:05:35,369
That's a... that's a lot of
money to be unaccounted for.

1190
01:05:35,402 --> 01:05:39,373
