out on the second day.

1202
01:06:15,710 --> 01:06:18,713
You might want to
read over that again.

1203
01:06:18,746 --> 01:06:21,583
You only work for us when
we say you work for us.

1204
01:06:21,616 --> 01:06:25,587
That doesn't include entertaining
the local civic leaders,

1205
01:06:25,620 --> 01:06:29,323
television appearances,
cocaine parties.

1206
01:06:29,356 --> 01:06:31,325
You really wanna go there?

1207
01:06:31,358 --> 01:06:33,728
You're stealing
from us, Charlie.

1208
01:06:33,761 --> 01:06:36,463
You get away with that,
you'd be the first.

1209
01:06:36,497 --> 01:06:40,234
See, that's my thing.

1210
01:06:40,267 --> 01:06:43,671
Going where no Black man
has ever gone before.

1211
01:06:48,510 --> 01:06:50,444
( sighs ) That's
a lot of money.

1212
01:06:50,477 --> 01:06:52,179
Money is no object.

1213
01:06:52,212 --> 01:06:55,449
Oh, shit, Charlie. That
wasn't meant literally.

1214
01:06:55,482 --> 01:06:58,786
